Files
-----

autocurrent.py
    Monitors and updates CF:ISCALE_S to keep EBPM signal in step with DCCT
    signal.

autosuper.py
    Lifted from iocbuilder/support.py, but probably not really wanted.

bcd.py
    No longer manages BCD (so a misnomer), but implements autogain.  Probably
    want to rename to autogain.py.

booster.py
    Some initial ideas for booster concentrator PVs, probably want to put all
    the booster PVs here.

bpm_list.py
    Loads list of SR BPMs from BPM list file.

concentrator.py
    Top level startup script, configures imports, loads remaining components,
    runs interactive IOC shell.

config.py
    Loads configuration file.

enabled.py
    Monitors SA positions and ENABLED flags, computes health waveform by taking
    missed updates into account.

injection.py
    New transfer efficiency calculations.

interlock.py
    Now cut to the bone, can be merged and dropped.

intervals.py
    Complex code for gathering distributed updates into common intervals.  New
    to this release, designed to be used throughout concentrator, needs a bit of
    cleaning.

maxadc.py
    A number of distributed waveforms together with special processing for
    SA:MAXADC.

monitor.py
    PV monitoring support, should mostly be obsoleted by intervals.py.

sa_waveforms.py
    An initial stab at some SA waveforms, but probably not sensible.

updater.py
    Used to manage some collections of updating waveforms.

waveforms.py
    Another random stab like sa_waveforms.py.


Concentrated waveforms
----------------------

FR:{STD,PP}{X,Y}    on BS-DI

PM:{X,Y,ADC}_{OFL,OFFSET}   on PM
    Need special offset on OFFSET values

SA:{CURRENT,X,Y,MAXADC}     on SA
    Need maximal severity on MAXADC

CF:ISCALE_S         asynchronous

{FT,FR,BN,IL}:ENABLE_S, CF:{ATTEN,AUTOSW,DETUNE}_S     asynchronous


Interval Controller
-------------------

Class hierarchy for interval controller::

    autosuper
        ControllerBase
            IntervalController
            TriggeredController
        ValueBase
            Value
                Value_PV
            Waveform
                Waveform_PV                 Internal waveform from list of PVs
                    Waveform_Out            Published waveform from PV list
                    MaskedWaveform
    IrregularController
    Controller_extra
    UpdateValue                             Internal to ValueBase
    UpdateWaveform                          Internal to ValueBase
    Waveform_Mean


PVs
---

These are the PVs we need to provide:


CS-DI-IOC-01:

HOSTNAME
WHOAMI

SR-DI-EBPM-01:

ATTENUATION:STAT
ATTENUATION_S
ATTENUATOR:DOWN
ATTENUATOR:UP

BPMID

COUNT_DISABLED
COUNT_ENABLED
COUNT_UNREACHABLE
ENABLED

ISCALE_INTERVAL
ISCALE_K
ISCALE_MIN
MAXADC
MAXADCID
MAXADCWF
MAXADC_PC
MODE:STAT
MODE_S

{BN,FR,FT}:ENABLE{,_S,:STAT}
IL:ENABLE

CF:{ATTEN,AUTOSW,DSC,GOLDEN_{X,Y}}{,_S,:STAT}
CK:DETUNE{,_S,:STAT}

SA:CURRENT{,:MEAN}
SA:{X,Y}{,:{{MIN,MAX}{,WF},MEAN,RESET,STD}}

FR:{PP,STD}{X,Y}
    BS-DI trigger, normally 5Hz but also supports other triggering.

PM:{ADC,X,Y}_{OFFSET,OFL}
    Triggered on PM.  OFFSET values need to be adjusted before being published.

SA:CURRENT{,:MEAN}
SA:{X,Y}:{{MAX,MIN}{,WF},MEAN,RESET,STD}
